# Owner playbook + _tools (session start)

When this chat starts, **read these first** (skim if already in context):

1. **`C:\Projects\_tools\OWNER-PLAYBOOK.md`** — how the owner wants replies, local-before-live, and verification
2. **`C:\Projects\_tools\SESSION-START.md`** — cross-project consistency index (read order, rule bundle, handoff)
3. **This repo:** ROADMAP (`docs/ROADMAP.md`), PRODUCT (`docs/PRODUCT.md` when scoping), and `.cursor/rules/`

Then **`C:\Projects\_tools\`** when you need shared scripts:

| Need | Path |
|------|------|
| Stop dev servers (handoff) | `C:\Projects\_tools\stop-dev-servers.ps1` |
| New project | `C:\Projects\_tools\new-project.ps1` |
| Cursor rule templates | `C:\Projects\_tools\templates\cursor-rules\` |
| Owner-approved UI patterns | `C:\Projects\_tools\DESIGN-FAVORITES.md` |

Per-project rules in this repo override the playbook when product-specific.
